res to be informative to the practitioner,\nand even more, stimulates her/him to carry on further research in main stream\nalgebraic logic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Aug 2015 08:11:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-25"}
